(501, 'App\\Models\\User', 2, 'updated', 'App\\Models\\Page', 18, '{\"content\":\"<p>Manage Your recruitment and related activities with ease and efficiently with ERA&rsquo;s E-Recruitment Solution.<\\/p>\\n<ul class=\\\"list-unstyled\\\">\\n<li class=\\\"d-table\\\"><i class=\\\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\\\"><\\/i>\\n<div class=\\\"d-table-cell\\\">Reach the widest candidate audience<\\/div>\\n<\\/li>\\n<li class=\\\"d-table\\\"><i class=\\\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\\\"><\\/i>\\n<div class=\\\"d-table-cell\\\">Meet all your talent acquisition challenges<\\/div>\\n<\\/li>\\n<li class=\\\"d-table\\\"><i class=\\\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\\\"><\\/i>\\n<div class=\\\"d-table-cell\\\">Artificial Intelligence (AI) can conduct evaluation tests of Job seekers with provision of automated result processing without any human interaction.<\\/div>\\n<\\/li>\\n<li class=\\\"d-table\\\"><i class=\\\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\\\"><\\/i>\\n<div class=\\\"d-table-cell\\\">Applicant Tracking Simplified<\\/div>\\n<\\/li>\\n<li class=\\\"d-table\\\"><i class=\\\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\\\"><\\/i>\\n<div class=\\\"d-table-cell\\\">Automate your processes<\\/div>\\n<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\"}', '{\"content\":\"<p><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.erainfotechbd.com\\/cms_assets\\/era e recruitment.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" \\/><br \\/><br \\/><br \\/><br \\/>Manage Your recruitment and related activities with ease and efficiency with ERA&rsquo;s E-Recruitment Solution.<\\/p>\\n<span class=\\\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\\\"><\\/span>\\n<ol>\\n<li>Wide Reach: E-recruitment allows organizations to reach a larger pool of potential candidates compared to traditional methods. By leveraging online platforms, job boards, social media, and company websites, organizations can attract candidates from different geographical locations, increasing the chances of finding t