(765, 'App\\Models\\User', 2, 'updated', 'App\\Models\\Page', 11, '{\"content\":\"<h1>Digital Customer Onboarding<\\/h1>\\n<br \\/>Our Digital Customer Onboarding solution allows your businesses to remotely verify the identity of customers using electronic documents and biometric data. This can help to streamline the customer onboarding process and reduce the need for physical paperwork and in-person verifications.<br \\/><br \\/><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.erainfotechbd.com\\/cms_assets\\/ekyc-01.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"img-fluid mx-auto d-block\\\" \\/>\"}', '{\"content\":\"<div class=\\\"container-fluid\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"row\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"col-sm-6\\\">\\n<p style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\">Key Features :<\\/p>\\n<ul style=\\\"list-style-type: square; font-size: 13px;\\\">\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">BFIU eKYC Guideline 2020 Compliant Solution.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Integrated Self &amp; Assisted Onboarding in a Single Platform.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Support for Multi-modal Biometric Verification (Face &amp; Fingerprint).<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Digital Customer Profiling and Automated Risk Grading.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Omni Channel eKYC Solution, Integration with CBS, ABS and Islamic CBS.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Integration with Bangladesh Election Commission Fingerprint Verification API &amp; SDK.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Integration with AML &amp; Sanction Screening System.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Integration with SMS &amp; Email Notification System.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Proprietary AI\\/ML Algorithms Developed by In-house Developer.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Dynamic Role Based Authentication &amp; Authorization.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Support for Major RDBMS (Oracle, PostgreSQL, MySQL