ffice connectivity with multiple external systems and delivery channels using web services.<\\/div>\\n<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\"}', '{\"content\":\"<div class=\\\"container-fluid\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"row\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"col-sm-6\\\">\\n<p style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\">Key Features :<\\/p>\\n<ul style=\\\"list-style-type: square; font-size: 13px;\\\">\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Single click CL processing &amp; Reporting according to Bangladesh Bank guidelines.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Single click CIB processing, Text File Generate &amp; Summary Report according to BB guidelines.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Single Screen Loan Closing operation with 360 view.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">All type of Schedule\\/Re-Structure\\/Re-Reschedule\\/Deferral and Customize Generation Facility.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Bulk\\/Individual Rate change and automated schedule impact facility.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Non-Schedule\\/LAD\\/LTD\\/Short Term Corporate Finance Product management.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Sundry\\/Suspense Management.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Back Value date based transaction facility &amp; reporting.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Multi mode collection\\/payment facility.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Day, Month, Quarter, Year End Related process and reporting.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">BL loan probable accrual process &amp; block charge Management.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Auto IBCA transaction facility for all transaction.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Back office excel voucher upload facility.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">Easy integration with third party solution through REST API.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<\\/div>\\n<div class=\\\"col-sm-6\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.er