(15, 'E-Tender', 'e-tender', '<div class=\"container-fluid\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n<p style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Key Features :</p>\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: square; font-size: 13px;\">\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Systems parameter setup.</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Raise Item Requisition and Approval.</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Prepare Tender and Edit.</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tender wise Evaluation Factor Setup.</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Creating Tender Committee.</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tender Publishing.</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bidder Signup / Registration.</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Physical Office Verification and Marking.</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Upload Subscription Fees Receipt.</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Subscription Fee&rsquo;s Payment Approval.</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tender List for Bidder.</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Downloading and Approving Schedule.</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bidding.</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tender Open.</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Technical Evaluation and Financial Evaluation.</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Create Short List.</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Negotiation and Price Review.</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Awarding the Appropriate bidder.</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Generating Work Order.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\"><img src=\"https://www.erainfotechbd.com/cms_assets/products/e_tender/image_etender.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid mx-auto d-block\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'e-tender', NULL, '2021-09-06 03:00:36', '2023-08-20 03:50:00'),
(16, 'ERP', 'erp', '<p>Our Orbit ERP (Enterprise Resource Planning) is a type of software that helps organizations manage and integrate their business processes and data, including finance, supply chain, manufacturing, human resources, and customer relationship management.&nbsp;</p>\n<img src=\"https://www.erainfotechbd.com/cms_assets/dasasdsa-01.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid mx-auto d-block\" />', 'erp', NULL, '2021-09-06 03:00:36', '2023-06-11 06:03:15'),
(17, 'HR Management', 'hr-management', '<div class=\"container-fluid\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n<p style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Key Features :</p>\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: square; font-size: 13px;\">\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">On Boarding</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Employee Profile Management</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Promotion, Increment, Transfer process</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Leave Management</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Attendance Management</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Performance Appraisal</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Employee Insurance Management</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Loans &amp; Advances</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tax Management</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Payroll Management</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bonus</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">TA/ DA</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Compliance &amp; Disciplinary Action</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Final Settlement</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">PF Management</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dynamic Report Generation (PDF &amp; Excel)</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Training Management</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\"><img src=\"https://www.erainfotechbd.com/cms_assets/products/hr/image_hr.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid mx-auto d-block\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'hr-management', NULL, '2021-09-06 03:00:36', '2023-08-20 04:09:35'),
(18, 'E-Recruitment', 'e-recruitment', '<div class=\"container-fluid\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Manage Your recruitment and related activities with ease and efficiency with ERA&rsquo;s E-Recruitment Solution.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wide Reach: E-recruitment allows organizations to reach a larger pool of potential candidates compared to traditional methods. By leveraging online platforms, job boards, social media, and company websites, organizations can attract candidates from different geographical locations, increasing the chances of finding the right talent.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-7\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Cost-Effectiveness:</strong> E-recruitment can be a cost-effective solution compared to traditional recruitment methods.<br /><br /><strong>Time Efficiency:</strong> E-recruitment streamlines the hiring process, saving significant time for recruiters.<br /><br /><strong>Enhanced Candidate Experience:</strong> E-recruitment offers a seamless and user-friendly experience for candidates.<br /><br /><strong>Improved Efficiency and Accuracy:</strong> E-recruitment tools, such as applicant tracking systems (ATS), enable recruiters to manage the recruitment workflow efficiently.<br /><br /><strong>Access to Diverse Talent:</strong> E-recruitment allows organizations to tap into a diverse talent pool. Online platforms enable targeted job advertisements, which can reach specific demographics or underrepresented groups.&nbsp;<br /><br /><strong>Data-Driven Decision Making:</strong> E-recruitment platforms often provide analytics and reporting capabilities, offering valuable insights into recruitment metrics. Integration with HR Systems: E-recruitment platforms can integrate with other HR systems, such as applicant tracking systems, human resource information systems (HRIS), or onboarding software.<br /><br /><strong>Integration with HR Systems:</strong> E-recruitment platforms can integrate with other HR systems, such as applicant tracking systems, human resource information systems (HRIS), or onboarding software.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-5\"><img src=\"https://www.erainfotechbd.com/cms_assets/era e recruitment.png\" alt=\"era e recruitment\" class=\"img-fluid mx-auto d-block\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'e-recruitment', NULL, '2021-09-06 03:00:36', '2023-07-18 02:00:02'),
(19, 'Artificial Intelligence', 'artificial-intelligence', '<h5><strong>Intelligent Solution for Intelligent People</strong></h5>\n<p>Artificial intelligence (AI) brings with it a promise of genuine human-to-machine interaction. When machines become intelligent, they can understand requests, connect data points and draw conclusions. AI based solutions in ERA-InfoTech Ltd includes Machine Learning (Supervised Learning), Deep Learning such Neural Network based solutions. Working for years in AI, we have a highly qualified team for providing solutions in developing, designing and integrating Artificial Intelligence techniques within the customer&rsquo;s business environment.</p>\n<h5><strong>Our Product line:</strong></h5>\n<p>AIDSS is a core <strong>AI</strong> based <strong>D</strong>ecision <strong>S</strong>upport <strong>S</strong>ystem engine which will provide data driven decisions based on the knowledge gained by the system from previously provided data more efficiently, effectively and easily!</p>\n<h5><strong>Features</strong></h5>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Designed to provide any type of data driven business decision for any organizations</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Assure the <strong>Highest Accuracy Rate</strong> based on best fit model</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Work with any number, length and type of training &lsquo;data attributes&rsquo; without customization</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Provides the best voted decision from the decisions produced by all the models</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Chat BOT</strong>: provide personalized support services to customers 24/7. &ldquo;CRM Chat BOT&mdash;AVA&rdquo; is a personalized customer service bot through which a company can provide service to its customer. It can be done through various options like Smart Apps, Web and Social Medias (e.g. Facebook)</p>\n<p><strong>Interview BOT</strong>: online recruitment of thousands of applicants at the same time. It speeds up The Interview Process &amp; shorten time to recruit.</p>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Makes life easy for both recruiter and applicant</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Unlimited user/examinee at a time</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Checking results autonomously</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Define question and answer time schedule, exam schedule etc.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Random questions to applicants</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Identify real examinee\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Face recognition; live movement detection (eye blink)</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Multiple person detection</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Resume from where applicant left</div>\n</li>\n</ul>', 'artificial-intelligence', NULL, '2021-09-06 03:00:36', '2021-10-14 11:02:52'),
(20, 'Internet of Things', 'internet-of-things', '<h5><strong>Auto Connect</strong></h5>\n<p>Auto Connect delivers the most advanced automobile tracking solutions available. Our products cover a wide range of scope from predictive maintenance to service automation, trucks &amp; fleet management solutions. The use of IoT made this system smooth.</p>\n<h5>Product Basket</h5>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Connected Car &amp; Car Servicing Automation</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Fleet Management</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Smart Truck</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h5><strong>Connected Car &amp; Service Automation</strong></h5>\n<p>Track the location, history, and health of your vehicle fleet in real-time from your apps. Know the condition of your car live using OBD2 connected though the internet. The owner as well the service center can see the status which shall help them predict any future threats of the vehicle. It is a huge system starting from problem diagnosis to ultimately taking service with inventory management, CRM etc.</p>\n<h5><strong>Features</strong></h5>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Real Time Dashboard</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Service Automation</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Predictive Maintenance</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Car Diagnosis and Location Tracking</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Road Side Assistance</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Collaboration with Customers</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Analytics on Customer Services</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h5><strong>Fleet Management (e-FLEET)</strong></h5>\n<p>Know exactly how much time your trucks are actually driving around, or how much downtime some of the trucks in your operations are experiencing. Now, there is an easy way to monitor and be in control of your operations, allowing you to improve efficiency, productivity and safety. The system also optimizes service intervals and lower the overall cost.</p>\n<h5><strong>Features</strong></h5>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Improved Efficiency</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Effective Cost Management</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Fleet Management from anywhere</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Quick Response to Queries</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Driver Behavior Analysis</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Quick Decision Based on Analysis</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h5><strong>Smart Truck</strong></h5>\n<p>Keep an eye on your trucks while they are driving for delivery. These includes car diagnosis and location tracking, recording of fuel consumption, theft control of goods and so on.</p>\n<h5><strong>Features</strong></h5>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">RFID for goods count</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">OBD for truck&rsquo;s health</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Fuel Level Detection</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Padlock for doors</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Goods Safety</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Surveillance Camera</div>\n</li>\n</ul>', 'internet-of-things', NULL, '2021-09-06 03:00:36', '2021-10-14 11:03:22'),
(21, 'Mobile Apps', 'mobile-apps', '<p>Mobile applications (also known as mobile apps) are software programs developed for mobile devices such as smartphones and tablets. They turn mobile devices into miniature powerhouses of function and fun. Many online entities have both mobile websites and mobile apps. In general, the difference lies in purpose: An app is usually smaller in scope than a mobile website, offers more interactivity, and presents more specific information in a format that&rsquo;s easy and intuitive to use on a mobile device.</p>\n<p>Before the widespread adoption of mobile devices, software was first developed to run on desktops and laptops, with a mobile version coming after. Tablet and smartphone usage are outstripping that of desktop computers and laptops, reflected in app sales trends. In fact, 258.2 billion apps were forecast to be downloaded in 2022. As a result, many developers have turned to a &ldquo;mobile-first&rdquo; approach, mirroring a similar trend in web design.</p>\n<p>ERA, with its robust experience in the software industry is capable of making any sorts of mobile application. As of now we have developed mobile application for different banking solutions, HR applications, etc.</p>', 'mobile-apps', NULL, '2021-09-06 03:00:36', '2021-10-14 11:03:58'),
(22, 'Outsourcing', 'outsourcing', '<p>ERA has a handful experience in working with different foreign companies. We customize our way of work with different companies as per their need.</p>\n<h5>What are we currently outsourcing?</h5>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Exchange the service, expertise</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Build a system</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Maintain the system</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Test the system</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>Key Strategy</h5>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Partnership\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Consultant based</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Partnership based</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Complete Product/Service\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">IoT</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\">Existing services (ERP, HR, Agent Banking)</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>Business Model</h5>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\"><strong>Time &amp; Material</strong>: Time &amp; Material (aka T&amp;M) model works mostly on projects where there are some unclear or evolving requirements. This is widely used where the projects are large with a lot of innovations are required.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\"><strong>Project Basis</strong>: This approach is just the opposite of the T&amp;M. The model is suitable for projects with a clear requirement like small, medium or large projects.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\"><strong>Dedicated Team</strong>: Dedicated team is always preferred by clients. This approach works mostly with the T&amp;M model. With a dedicated team, clients have the ease to monitor &amp; manage remotely which includes development process, meeting on a regular basis.</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"d-table\"><i class=\"bi bi-check-lg px-3 text-primary lh-lg\"></i>\n<div class=\"d-table-cell\"><strong>Hybrid Model</strong>: In some complex development process we need a mixture of all the process. These are mostly special cases which rely on several factors. At this point we need apply both T&amp;M and Dedicated team model. This is Hybrid model.</div>\n</li>\n</ul>', 'outsourcing', NULL, '2021-09-06 03:00:36', '2021-10-14 11:04:32');
